        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">I think they only increased the DOT's by one tick.</P><P>The way they came up with the 18 seconds is that at the end of each tick (6 seconds), if the MOB is moving they only take 66% damage.</P><P>18 seconds is three ticks. So if they lose 33% for each tick, then after three ticks you reach the point where your DOT has lost the same amount of damage as has been added during the patch.</P><P>Dryzza Souldrinker of Emerald Circle of Chaos<BR>Level 50 Necromancer of Ayonae Ro<BR>Evil Mistress of the Dead<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
